=== 人物创作和演员选择 ===
据[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]日间节目高级副总裁[[喜来登·卡卢里亚|喜来登·卡卢里亚]]（{{lang|en|Sheraton Kalouria}}）透露<ref name="Kalouria1">{{cite journal | url = https://variety.com/2000/scene/news/nbc-days-abc-s-kalouria-1117781385/ | title = NBC's days ABC's Kalouria | last = Bernstein | first = Paula | date = 2000-05-09 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | archivedate = 2019-10-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191030220531/https://variety.com/2000/scene/news/nbc-days-abc-s-kalouria-1117781385/}}</ref>，《激情》挑选演员时有意不考虑肤色差异，以此确保演员族群多元化，这样最能体现美国民族和种族的多样化。卡卢里亚认为，《激情》中的[[罗素家族_(激情)|罗素一家]]是非裔美国人家族，洛佩兹-菲茨杰拉德（{{lang|en|Lopez-Fitzgerald}}）一家是西班牙裔，这正是本剧能在众多肥皂剧中脱颖而出的根本原因。<ref name="Jet1">{{cite book | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=H74DAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=liz+sanbourne+passions+casting&source=bl&ots=kQw2SvsX0M&sig=6A_4zjJje4v2q6DaH-k1BZgU-E8&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=liz%20sanbourne%20passions%20casting&f=false | title = Soap Opera ‘Passions’ Keeps Igniting Fervor Among Daytime Viewers | date = 2003-01-13 | work = Jet | publisher = Johnson Publishing Company | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131182427/https://books.google.com/books?id=H74DAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=liz%2Bsanbourne%2Bpassions%2Bcasting&source=bl&ots=kQw2SvsX0M&sig=6A_4zjJje4v2q6DaH-k1BZgU-E8&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj_sf_x3q7KAhVC5iYKHY8rBH84ChDoAQgqMAM | archivedate = 2016-01-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

