22 | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。迪维斯本是参与另一档肥皂剧试镜，但该剧制作人建议他参演《激情》<ref name="Initially">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.buddytv.com/info/charles-divins-info.aspx | title = Charles Divins | publisher = BuddyTV | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171222052017/http://www.buddytv.com/info/charles-divins-info.aspx | archivedate = 2017-12-22 | accessdate = 2017-12-22}}</ref>。据本人透露，此次演出机会对他来说就像“表演奖学金”<ref name="casting3">{{cite episode | series = Soap Talk | network = SOAPnet | airdate = 2009-08-30}}</ref>。

=== 人物特征和演出反响 ===
据《激情》的官方网站介绍，查德起初是“街头小子”<ref name="Character1">{{cite web | url = http://www.nbc.com/passions/background/pgv_passions_background.html | title = Show Background | publisher = [[全国广播公司|NBC]] | archivedate = 2000-08-15 | deadurl = yes | accessdate =2000-08-15| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20000815092052/https://www.nbc.com/passions/background/pgv_passions_background.html}}</ref>，《[[湾区报导|湾区报导]]》（''{{lang|en|Bay Area Reporter}}''）的戴维·亚历山大·纳赫莫德（{{lang|en|David Alexander Nahmod}}）认为他属于“街坊中的硬汉”<ref name="Hood">{{cite news | first = David Alexander | last = Nahmod | url = http://www.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=television&article=80 | title = 'Passions' pushes the envelope | newspaper = Bay Area Reporter | publisher = BAR Media, Inc. | date = 2007-02-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051822/http://www.ebar.com/arts/art_article.php?sec=television&article=80 | archivedate = 2017-12-22 | accessdate = 2017-12-22}}</ref>。斯瓦比觉得查德“才华横溢、雄心勃勃，充满冒险精神和激情”，强烈的防卫心理是“对好人与坏人刻板定型的反抗”<ref name="Character2">{{cite web | archivedate = 2017-12-22 | work = Soaps.com | date = 2007-12-06 | url = https://soaps.sheknows.com/passions/news/1292/former-chad-says-goodbye-to-passions-character/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171222052906/http://soaps.sheknows.com/passions/news/1292/former-chad-says-goodbye-to-passions-character | title = Former Chad Says Goodbye to Passions Character | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。查德起初只是“[[西蒙妮·罗素|西蒙妮]]和惠特尼喜欢上的男人”<ref name="Jet1" />，但迪维斯的加入促使人物戏份扩张<ref name="Casting2" />。{{lang|en|Soaps.com}}（意为“肥皂剧.{{lang|en|com}}”）网站发文称，迪维斯令人物从“西岸音乐制作人变成雄心勃勃但又纠结不已的克兰家族继承人”。查德的剧情主要关注他与惠特尼和文森特·克拉克森的感情，剧情一度表明惠特尼是他同父异母的妹妹，文森特则是他侄子。<ref name="Casting2" />退出节目后，斯瓦比对查德的情节发展感到失望<ref name="Character2" />。

查德和文森特发生性关系的情节颇具争议而且评价欠佳，但迪维斯认为[[性向认同|性向认同]]矛盾和挣扎是人物情节至关重要的部分<ref name="OutinHollywood" />。节目拍摄期间，他曾表示有意进一步探讨查德对性向的抗拒<ref name="Hood" />，觉得人物难以接受自身性取向是《激情》的关键要素<ref name="OutinHollywood">{{cite news | first = Greg | last = Hernandez | accessdate = 2018-08-25 | deadurl = yes | url = http://blogs.dailynews.com/outinhollywood/2007/02/24/a-lover-to-be-revealed-tuesday/ | title = A lover to be revealed Tuesday on "Passions" | work = Out in Hollywood | publisher = Digital First Media | date = 2007-02-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180825114907/http://blogs.dailynews.com/outinhollywood/2007/02/24/a-lover-to-be-revealed-tuesday/ | archivedate = 2018-08-25}}</ref>。迪维斯在接受采访时称，节目会明确表现“男人亲密关系”，他对拍摄这类镜头感到有些不自在，但觉得这是锻炼演技的好机会<ref name="Hood" />。他还希望能让人物尽可能显得“真实且脚踏实地”，注重表现查德是如何理解并接受自身性取向<ref name="Philly">{{cite web | first = Ross | last = von Metzke | deadurl = no | url = https://philadelphia.edgemedianetwork.com/story.php?ch=entertainment&sc=television&sc2=news&sc3=&id=40814&ten_minutes_with_charles_divins | title = Ten Minutes with Charles Divins | work = Edge Media Network | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170928005417/http://philadelphia.edgemedianetwork.com/entertainment/television/news//40814/ten_minutes_with_charles_divins | publisher = Edge Publications Inc. | date = 2007-03-17 | archivedate = 2017-09-28}}</ref>。

为演好角色，迪维斯与同性恋友人探讨剧情，了解他们对如何真诚表现人物的看法<ref name="OutinHollywood" />。[[奧花·雲費|奧花·雲費]]曾在《[[奥普拉·温弗里秀|奥普拉·温弗里秀]]》讨论“与同性发生关系，但却坚信自己不是同性恋”的心理，对迪维斯理解查德很有帮助<ref name="Philly" />。迪维斯直到正式开演四天前拿到剧本时才知道人物性向发展<ref name="OutinHollywood" />，他对查德与男人的外遇表示惊讶，但考虑到《激情》是肥皂剧，剧情发展风格注定容易出现非常戏剧化的变化<ref name="Hood" />。部分剧迷希望查德和惠特尼在一起，所以对人物的外遇非常不满，但迪维斯认可电视剧在日间电视节目中纳入黑人同性恋的做法，让{{lang|en|[[LGBT|LGBT]]}}议题得到更多出现在电视及日常社会生活的机会，他也不担心出演这样的角色会有什么不良后果<ref name="Philly" />。部分演员不认可查德的人物特点和剧情，饰演[[伊芙·罗素|伊芙·罗素]]的[[特蕾西·罗斯|特蕾西·罗斯]]（{{lang|en|Tracey Ross}}）就自认一直不喜欢涉及所谓乱伦的剧情<ref name="Ross">{{cite web | archivedate = 2018-07-13 | url = https://soaps.sheknows.com/passions/news/2133/tracey-ross-looks-back-at-her-time-on-passions/ | first = Lori | title = Tracey Ross Looks Back at Her Time on Passions | website = Soaps.com | date = 2008-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180713232248/http://soaps.sheknows.com/passions/news/2133/tracey-ross-looks-back-at-her-time-on-passions | last = Wilson | accessdate = 2020-09-12}}</ref>，但出演文森特·克拉克森的菲利普·杰娜玛丽（{{lang|en|Phillip Jeanmarie}}）表示，很高兴能成为打破禁忌的故事一员<ref name="Sex">{{cite web | url = https://daytimeconfidential.com/2009/07/30/dc-exclusive-passions-villain-phillip-jeanmarie-talks-workshop-gay-firsts-and-reilly | title = DC Exclusive: Passions Villain Phillip Jeanmarie Talks "Workshop", Gay Firsts and Reilly | last = Giddens | first = Jamey | date = 2009-07-30 | work = Daytime Confidential | publisher = Confidential Media, Inc. | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180714021817/https://daytimeconfidential.com/2009/07/30/dc-exclusive-passions-villain-phillip-jeanmarie-talks-workshop-gay-firsts-and-reilly | archivedate = 2018-07-14}}</ref>。

== 剧情发展 ==
查德·哈里斯-克兰于1999年9月23日首度登场，他在得知自己是养子后从洛杉矶搬到虚构小镇“哈蒙尼”（{{lang|en|Harmony}}，意为“和谐”）寻找亲生父母。查德本是洛杉矶的音乐制作人，已经与拉托亚·哈里斯（{{lang|en|Latoya Harris}}）结婚，但她不愿离开朋友和家人陪丈夫前往哈蒙尼。查德在哈蒙尼找到奥维尔·帕金斯（{{lang|en|Orville Perkins}}）和克里斯托·哈里斯（{{lang|en|Crystal Harris}}），两人能为他寻找亲人提供线索。奥维尔年势已高，以为查德是伊芙·罗素与克兰实业首席执行官朱利安·克兰（{{lang|en|Julian Crane}}）失散已久的儿子，自称有证据证明血缘。伊芙已有美满稳定的生活，一心只想掩盖过去，于是放火烧掉奥维尔的房子，里面即便有任何证据也已付之一炬，并将奥维尔送进养老院。克里斯托是伊芙与朱利安交往及后来怀孕期间的闺蜜，现在是爵士歌手，自称拥有查德出生及父母的信息，但还没来得及把信息告知查德就被法国贩毒集团刺客安托万（{{lang|en|Antoine}}）杀害，但安托万其实杀错了人，误将克里斯托当成社交名媛谢里丹·克兰（{{lang|en|Sheridan Crane}}）。

查德在此期间结识惠特尼·罗素（{{lang|en|Whitney Russell}}），两人堕入情网，但惠特尼的妹妹西蒙妮也对他一见钟情。惠特尼和西蒙妮的父母都不同意女儿和他交往，伊芙觉得查德就像她少女时代遇到的朱利安，觉得他不利于女儿成长，所以不同意他们交往，但惠特尼还是私下与查德热恋，两人多次发生性关系，查德同时还假装与西蒙妮相恋，为他和惠特尼的关系掩护。三角恋情一直持续到西蒙妮发现男友和姐姐做爱，她马上公开宣布分手，并将他和姐姐的关系广而告之。2003年，惠特尼险被拉托亚谋杀，然后发现她是查德的妻子，情感关系因此破裂。

[[丽兹·桑伯恩|丽兹·桑伯恩]]（{{lang|en|Liz Sanbourne}}）是伊芙父母领养的妹妹，但她非常憎恨伊芙，经过她的安排，伊芙昔日与朱利安的恋情在全镇范围曝光，导致众人都以为查德是伊芙和朱利安的儿子。查德和惠特尼的关系变成乱伦，开始成为《激情》的主线。惠特尼发现已怀上查德的孩子，她主动和[[福克斯·克兰|福克斯·克兰]]交往，以此营造腹中孩子属于福克斯的假象，希望自己和孩子免受乱伦的耻辱。生下儿子后，她马上让福克斯安排将孩子送去领养机构。朱利安和伊芙，以及{{lang|en|T·C}}·罗素（{{lang|en|T. C. Russell}}）和丽兹争相领养惠特尼的孩子，但最终是查德获得监护权，希望靠孩子与惠特尼重归于好，两人决定借爵士音乐家[[邁爾士·戴維斯|邁爾士·戴維斯]]的名字为孩子取名迈尔斯·戴维斯·哈里斯（{{lang|en|Miles Davis Harris}}）。2005年《激情》暑期大汇演期间，惠特尼与查德在海啸期间发生性关系，承认他才是迈尔斯的生父。2006年《激情》暑期大汇演的剧情取名“仇杀”（{{lang|en|''Vendetta''}}），主要讲述[[阿利斯泰尔·克兰|阿利斯泰尔·克兰]]（{{lang|en|Alistair Crane}}）设法把惠特尼、查德在内的许多哈蒙尼居民引到罗马。查德在罗马期间从[[小报_(版式)|小报]]主编康奈尔（{{lang|en|JT Cornell}}）手中拿到自己的出生证明，原来他是当年阿利斯泰尔强奸丽兹所生。查德和惠特尼随即成婚，决定一起把儿子养大，并为孩子更名迈尔斯·哈里斯-克兰。

查德此前已经开始与小报记者文森特·克拉克森（{{lang|en|Vincent Clarkson}}）交往并多次发生性关系，两人在“仇杀”剧情开始前后发生关系，具体时间不明，惠特尼对此一无所知。与惠特尼举办婚礼后，查德继续保持与文森特的关系，根本不知道文森特正是伊芙与朱利安的儿子，所以既是他的弟弟，又是妻子的哥哥，还是他的叔父。查德也没发现文森特其实是有双重人格的[[雙性人|雙性人]]，另一重人格还以瓦莱丽·戴维斯（{{lang|en|Valerie Davis}}）之名在克兰实业工作，是副总裁[[特蕾莎·洛佩兹-菲茨杰拉德|特蕾莎·洛佩兹-菲茨杰拉德]]（{{lang|en|Theresa Lopez-Fitzgerald}}）的行政助理。查德向好友[[帕洛玛·洛佩兹-菲茨杰拉德|帕洛玛·洛佩兹-菲茨杰拉德]]（{{lang|en|Paloma Lopez-Fitzgerald}}）和[[诺亚·贝内特|诺亚·贝内特]]（{{lang|en|Noah Bennett}}）承认外遇，同时反复坚称自己不是同性恋，与文森特之间完全只是性关系。惠特尼怀上第二个孩子后越来越怀疑查德有外遇，文森特对查德继续同惠特尼上床妒火中烧，于是设法让惠特尼看到他和查德在[[同志酒吧|同志酒吧]]后面性交。惠特尼马上离开查德，后者从此也与文森特保持距离，直到两人帮助特蕾莎和伊森·温思罗普（{{lang|en|Ethan Winthrop}}）重归于好时才开始和解。2007年8月28日，查德为保护伊森被亲生父亲阿利斯泰尔所杀，并在临死前宣告他对惠特尼及两个孩子的爱。

== 评价和影响 ==
查德的多段恋情都可能牵涉乱伦，媒体为此得出耸人听闻的结论：哈蒙尼就是那些“半兄弟姐妹上床”的地方<ref name="Tulsa">{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-11-26 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | url = https://tulsaworld.com/archives/daytime-dial-life-is-far-from-harmony--ous-for/article_fb4c1138-affc-586a-848c-f5a811bb9e56.html | title = Daytime Dial: Life is far from 'Harmony'-ous for Brook Kerr's Whitney | last = Block | first = Dana | date = 2006-05-21 | work = Tulsa World | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20161126185132/http://www.tulsaworld.com/archives/daytime-dial-life-is-far-from-harmony--ous-for/article_fb4c1138-affc-586a-848c-f5a811bb9e56.html}}</ref>，《[[肥皂剧文摘|肥皂剧文摘]]》（''{{lang|en|Soap Opera Digest}}''）甚至宣称2006年揭露惠特尼和查德没有血缘关系的情节“极其令人震惊”<ref name="Shocking2">{{cite web | date = 2007-12-18 | work = Soap Opera Digest | publisher = American Media, Inc. | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | url = https://www.soapoperadigest.com/content/passionss-most-shocking-secrets-bra-look-back-those-memorable-revelations-rocked-harmony-0/ | title = A Look Back at Those Memorable Revelations That Rocked Harmony  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170928060306/http://www.soapoperadigest.com/content/passionss-most-shocking-secrets-bra-look-back-those-memorable-revelations-rocked-harmony-0/ | archivedate = 2017-09-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|Soapdom.com}}（意为“肥皂剧迷{{lang|en|.com}}”）网站断言，这些剧情是迪维斯展现演技的机遇，证明他比斯瓦比更出色<ref name="Soapdom">{{cite web | archivedate = 2017-01-04 | accessdate = 2017-01-04 | url = http://www.soapdom.com/Busted-to-Blissful/october-2004-passions.html | title = October 2004 ~ Passions | last = Coker | first = Lesleyann | date = 2004-10-07 | publisher = Soapdom.com | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170104104905/http://www.soapdom.com/Busted-to-Blissful/october-2004-passions.html}}</ref>。

媒体对查德的确切性取向看法不一。布伦特·哈丁格（{{lang|en|Brent Hartinger}}）认为他是“尚未出柜的双性恋”<ref name="Logo">{{cite web | url = http://www.newnownext.com/new-eastenders-character-finally-brings-diversity-to-soaps/11/2009/ | title = New 'EastEnders' Character (Finally) Brings Diversity to Soaps | last = Hartinger | first = Brent | date = 2009-11-03 | website = NewNowNext.com | publisher = Logo TV | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170928005343/http://www.newnownext.com/new-eastenders-character-finally-brings-diversity-to-soaps/11/2009/ | archivedate = 2017-09-28}}</ref>，《湾区报导》称他是黑人男同性恋<ref name="Hood" />。{{lang|en|NewNowNext.com}}网站刊文评选“最受欢迎男同性恋电视角色”，迪维斯诠释的查德便是其中选项<ref name="Favorite">{{cite web | url = http://www.newnownext.com/favorite-gay-male-tv-character-poll/ | title = Favorite Gay (Male) TV Character Poll | website = NewNowNext.com | publisher = Logo TV | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170114170208/http://www.newnownext.com/favorite-gay-male-tv-character-poll/ | archivedate = 2017-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-09-12}}</ref>。{{lang|en|Welovesoaps.net}}（意为“我们爱肥皂剧{{lang|en|.net}}”）网站刊登罗杰·纽科姆（{{lang|en|Roger Newcomb}}）的文章，质疑查德不是真正的同性恋，因为文森特是有双重人格的双性人，和查德发生关系的正是他化身女人的一面<ref name="Love">{{cite web | url = https://www.welovesoaps.net/2008/07/gaylesbianbisexual-television.html | title = History of Gay/Lesbian/Bisexual Television Characters | last = Newcomb | first = Roger | date = 2008-07-07 | website = We Love Soaps | archivedate = 2018-03-20 | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180320063315/http://www.welovesoaps.net/2008/07/gaylesbianbisexual-television.html}}</ref>。[[喬爾·麥克哈爾|喬爾·麥克哈爾]]在{{lang|en|[[E!|E!]]}}频道电视剧《[[汤_(电视剧)|汤]]》（{{lang|en|''The Soup''}}）中恶搞查德坚称他不是同性恋、只是和文森特性交的片段，将人物称作“不是同性恋的查德”。迪维斯在《汤》第五季第一集[[客串|客串]]出镜，在剧中向麥克哈爾坚称他不是查德，既没死也不是同性恋。<ref name="The Soup">{{cite episode | title = Episode 1 | series = The Soup | network = [[E!|E!]] | airdate = 2008-01-04 | season = 5}}</ref>

《激情》是历史上第一部显示两名男子做爱的日间电视剧，但查德和文森特配对引来的媒体关注不及《[[地球照转|地球照转]]》（''{{lang|en|As the World Turns}}''）和《[[只此一生|只此一生]]》（''{{lang|en|One Life to Live}}''）的同性恋情<ref name="Sex" />。凯尔·布坎南（{{lang|en|Kyle Buchanan}}）在掴客网发文，称剧中错综复杂的乱伦恋令人费解到要发疯，觉得即便在电视史上也是非常疯狂的剧情<ref name="CrazyCucu">{{cite web | deadurl = no | url = https://gawker.com/5063983/the-creator-of-the-best-tv-show-ever-passions-has-died | title = The Creator of The Best TV Show Ever, 'Passions,' Has Died | last = Buchanan | first = Kyle | date = 2008-10-15 | website = Gawker | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180427020037/http://gawker.com/5063983/the-creator-of-the-best-tv-show-ever-passions-has-died | archivedate = 2018-04-27 | accessdate = 2020-09-12}}</ref>。{{lang|en|Soaps.com}}对乱伦剧情青眼有加，认为肥皂剧的世界往往风平浪静、缺乏惊喜，但《激情》勇于打破常规，以独特的视角和热情引发争议<ref name="Viewers">{{cite web | url = https://soaps.sheknows.com/passions/news/607/passions-new-controversy/ | title = Passions' New Controversy | date = 2007-03-09 | work = Soaps.com | archivedate = 2017-09-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170928005740/http://soaps.sheknows.com/passions/news/607/passions-new-controversy | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|NewNowNext.com}}网站称赞剧情确保日间电视节目有更多{{lang|en|LGBT}}有色人种角色出场的机会<ref name="Logo" />，边缘媒体网的罗斯·冯·梅兹（{{lang|en|Ross von Metze}}）称，《激情》是在冒险尝试其他电视节目都以失败告终的路子<ref name="Philly" />。

观众对查德和文森特露骨的性爱镜头看法不一。部分观众认为这些镜头“骇人听闻”，不适合日间电视节目，其中一名观众不无讽刺地表示，《激情》“一如既往地向当今世界的人们传授日常生活经验”。{{lang|en|Soaps.com}}发文支持节目中的同性性爱镜头，称过去那些男女间性行为的镜头就从未招来指摘。<ref name="Viewers"/>

部分评论批评查德和文森特的恋情，《[[风城时报|风城时报]]》（''{{lang|en|Windy City Times}}''）就觉得这段情节过于鲁莽甚至“令人发指”<ref name="Windy">{{Cite web | archivedate = 2018-07-02 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-12 | url = http://www.windycitymediagroup.com/lgbt/View-Racial-vs-gay-diversity-in-daytime-TV/21128.html | title = View: Racial vs. gay diversity in daytime TV – Gay Lesbian Bi Trans News Archive – Windy City Times | last = Davis | first = Herndon L. | date = 2009-05-01 | newspaper = Windy City Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180702035724/http://www.windycitymediagroup.com/lgbt/View-Racial-vs-gay-diversity-in-daytime-TV/21128.html}}</ref>。《[[板岩_(杂志)|板岩]]》（''{{lang|en|Slate}}''）杂志的[[塔内西·科茨|塔内西·科茨]]（{{lang|en|Ta-Nehisi Coates}}）称，观看《激情》的黑人观众也不喜欢这段剧情<ref name="OntheDownLow">{{cite web | title = A Low-Down Crying Shame | last = Coates | first = Ta-Nehisi | date = 2007-03-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200605162044/https://slate.com/technology/2007/03/why-the-myth-of-on-the-down-low-refuses-to-die.html | archivedate = 2020-06-05 | journal = Slate | publisher = The Slate Group | deadurl = no | url = http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2007/03/a_lowdown_crying_shame.html | accessdate = 2020-06-05}}</ref>。迈克·佩里加德（{{lang|en|Mike Perigard}}）在《[[波士顿先驱报|波士顿先驱报]]》（''{{lang|en|Boston Herald}}''）发文，严厉谴责剧中女同性恋友蕾·托马斯（{{lang|en|Rae Thomas}}）在查德和文森特的私情暴露后被杀，他认为此举完全是因为节目只敢保持少数角色是同性恋，“超额”的就要死<ref name="BostonHerald">{{Cite news | last = Perigard | first = Mark | publisher = Herald Media Inc. | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-07-02 | url = http://www.bostonherald.com/2007/02/passions_exceeds_gay_quota_kills_character | title = 'Passions' exceeds gay quota, kills character | newspaper = Boston Herald | archivedate = 2018-07-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180702035552/http://www.bostonherald.com/2007/02/passions_exceeds_gay_quota_kills_character}}</ref>。

